high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter top.
Pick up the knife next to the spatula.
Walk towards the wall to your left then turn left so that you are facing the wooden counter top across from the refrigerator.
Cut the potato, in the rear, right corner of the counter top, into slices.
Turn around and walk to the microwave cart, next to the refrigerator.
Set the knife down, to the right of the spoon, on the microwave cart.
Turn back around, facing the wooden counter top with the sliced potato on it.
Pick up one of the potato slices and place it on the counter next to the green container, near the edge.
Walk to your left, towards the oven, turning to your right at the sink.
Place the potato slice into the sink, turn the water on to rinse the potato off, turn the water off, and pick the potato slice back up.
Turn to your right and walk back towards the wall, stopping at the microwave and turning to your right.
Place the potato slice next to the spoon, and in front of the knife, on the black microwave cart.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean potato slice on the microwave cart.

high_descs: Turn around and head to the table on the right
Grab the knife on the table
Turn around and head to the table in the corner
Cut the potato on the table in slices
Turn around and head to the microwave
Place the knife down near the tomato on the black table
Turn around and head to the table
Pick up one of the potato slices
Turn left and stop at the sink
Wash the potato in the sink and take it out
Turn around and head to the microwave
Place the potato near the knife and tomato on the black table
anns.task_desc: Moving a sliced potato to the black table

high_descs: Turn left then face the counter with the knife on your left.
Pick up the knife from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the counter with the sponge on your left.
Slice the potato on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and head towards the microwave in front of you.
Place the knife on the left plate on the counter in front of you.
Turn around and face the counter with the potato on top of it.
Take a potato slice from the counter in front of you.
Turn left then face the sink on your right.
Wash the potato slice in the sink in front of you and take it out.
Turn around and head towards the microwave in front of you.
Place the potato slice on the plate with the knife in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean potato slice on a plate.

high_descs: turn around towards the table
pick up the knife
turn around towards the table
slice the potato on the table
turn around towards the oven
drop the knife in front of the oven
turn around and head for the table
pick up a potato slice
move left towards the sink
wash the potato in the sink
turn around and head for the microwave
place the slice in front of the microwave
anns.task_desc: place a potato slice in front of the microwave

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the yellow knife next to the spatula on the counter.
Pick up the yellow knife next to the spatula on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the potato on the counter in the opposite corner of the room.
Cut up the potato on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the microwave to the right of the fridge.
Place the knife to the right of the spoon on the table.
Turn around and walk to the cut up potato on the counter.
Pick up a piece of the potato from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse the piece of potato in the sink and then pick up the piece of potato from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the microwave to the right of the fridge.
Place the piece of potato to the right of the spoon on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed piece of potato on the table to the right of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward to the oven, turn left to face the counter.
Take the knife to the left of the spatula on the counter.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the counter above the green bin.
Cut the potato on the counter into slices.
Turn around, go forward and to the right to the stand to the right of the fridge with the microwave.
Put the knife on the stand to the right of the spoon.
Turn left, go forward to the wall, turn left, go forward to the counter above the green bin.
Take a slice of potato from the counter.
Turn left, go forward, turn right at the sink.
Wash the potato slice in the sink. Take the potato from the sink.
Turn right, go forward, turn right to go to the stand with the microwave.
Put the potato on the stand to the right of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed slice of potato on a stand.
